title: Mack Trade, Season Superlatives FROM LONDON
itunes:title: Mack Trade, Season Superlatives FROM LONDON
description:
A boat filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler & Chris Wesseling – detail their first day in London (1:20)! While floating down the River Thames, the heroes discuss the Raiders most recent moves, including the blockbuster Khalil Mack trade (4:25), parting ways with Martavis Bryant (15:00) and acquiring AJ McCarron from the Bills (17:30). The heroes then converse about Jerick McKinnon’s season-ending injury (18:50), Nick Foles starting against the Falcons (21:00), noteworthy players that were cut (23:20) and finally, season superlatives (32:30).
